<h1>Your event is live</h1>

<p>Hi,</p>

<p>Thanks a lot for using HopHub!</p>

<p>The event "<strong><%= @event.name %></strong>" has been confirmed and is now active.</p>

<p>Please share the following link with potential participants:</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_url(@event) %>" class="button">View event page</a></p>

<p>If you want to update or delete the event, please use the following secret link. Please keep this link to yourself and do not share it with others:</p>

<div class="secret-link"><a href="<%= edit_event_url(@event, admin_token: @event.admin_token, locale: I18n.locale) %>"><%= edit_event_url(@event, admin_token: @event.admin_token, locale: I18n.locale) %></a></div>

<p>The event and all its offers and requests will automatically be deleted after the configured end date (<strong><%= l @event.end_date.to_date, format: :long, locale: I18n.locale %></strong>).</p>

<p>Happy sharing, you are awesome!</p>

<p class="signoff">Kind regards from the HopHub platform.</p>
